    <td class="rowodd" valign="top" width="2000">Bug fixes/Improvements:<br>1. Server-specific auto-join settings were not processed properly.<br>2. Characters other than alpha-numerics and underscore could not be used in command aliases.<br>3. Command &quot;ALIAS&quot; will now accept definitions with and without leading slashes: &quot;/alias /j /join&quot;, &quot;/alias j join&quot;.</td>
</tr>
